title: Ep 1997 - Champaklal ki Sabak
shortDesc: Jethalal calls Nattu kaka and informs him that he has reached Surat. Bagha tells Nattu kaka that Champaklal taught a lesson to the goons who had teased Bawri.

title: Ep 1998 - Mission Saafsafai
shortDesc: Bhide invites his neighbors to Jethalal’s shop. He tells them that they must teach a lesson to the goons who often tease Bawri. Sodhi proposes a plan to punish the goons.

title: Ep 1999 - Gokuldham ke Gunde
shortDesc: Sodhi and his neighbors plan to teach a lesson to the goons teasing Bawri. Bawri introduces Sodhi and his friends to the real goons. Bagha asks the goons to stay away from Bawri in the future.

title: Ep 2000 - Gokuldham Behind The Bars
shortDesc: Police arrest Sodhi, Bhide, Aiyer and rest of the Gokuldham society men and put them behind bars. They assume all of them as goons. Daya enters the police station and clears the confusion.

title: Ep 2001 - Gokuldham Society Plans For Independence Day
shortDesc: Sundar calls Jethalal and informs him that he would come to Mumbai on the occasion of Raksha Bandhan. Members of Gokuldham Society decide to have flag hoisting ceremony on the Independence Day.

title: Ep 2002 - Gaane Ki Azaadi
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham Society gather to participate in the flag hoisting ceremony. Abdul gets the honour to hoist the National Flag. Later, Tapu Sena throws a challenge to all the married couples

title: Ep 2003 - Independence Day in Gokuldham
shortDesc: In today’s episode, the members of Gokuldham Society continue their Independence Day Celebration by singing various patriotic songs. Jethalal is anxiously waiting for his turn to sing a patriotic song

title: Ep 2004 - Gokuldham Society Sends Rakhis to Indian Soldiers
shortDesc: All women of Gokuldham society gather to plan for the day of ‘Raksha Bandhan’.  Daya requests Jethalal to send a gift-hamper to the army soldiers who are at the borders of the country.

title: Ep 2005 - Sundar ka Gift
shortDesc: Daya and her neighbors prepare a gift-hamper. They decide to gift the hamper to the army men on the occasion of raksha-bandhan. Sundar comes to Jethalal’s house to meet his sister.

title: Ep 2006 - Raksha Bandhan with Soldiers
shortDesc: Surbhi bring her daughter Khushi to Jethalal’s house. Khushi ties rakhis to all the members of Tapu sena. On the other hand, Sodhi and all women of Gokuldham society meet the brave Indian soldiers

title: Ep 2007 - Jethalal ka Promise
shortDesc: Bagha requests Jethalal to pay him his next month’s salary in advance. He informs Jethalal that he spent all his salary on Bawri. Later, Jethalal promises Daya to fulfil her wishes in the future.

title: Ep 2008 - Taarak ki Samasya
shortDesc: Women of Gokuldham society plan to visit a jewelry exhibition. They requests Taarak and Jethalal to accompany them to the venu.

title: Ep 2009 - Gokuldham Society Visits Jewelry Exhibition
shortDesc: Daya and all her neighbours are excited to visit a jewelry exhibition. Taarak Mehta alerts all the men of Gokuldham Society that their wives may request them to buy expensive jewelry. Jethalal and his neighbours visit the jewelry exhibition

title: Ep 2010 - Hiralal Ka Jewelry Exhibition
shortDesc: Daya and her neighbors enter the jewelry exhibition. Jethalal introduces Hiralal and his wife to all the members of Gokuldham Society.

title: Ep 2011 - Daya Wants Diamond Studded Saree
shortDesc: Daya and the women of Gokuldham society are enticed by an expensive diamond studded saree displayed in the exhibition. Daya requests Jethalal to bring home the saree on rent for a day.
